      "x": 2320,
      "y": 1065,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 170,
      "text": "Shown on \"Move to Jobs\" when the lead's\nsituation maps to requires_estimate\n(Exploring, New System, Upgrade).\n\n\"This job type typically requires an estimate.\nMove to Jobs anyway, or move to Sales for\nthe estimate workflow?\"\n\n• Move to Jobs (proceed — override logged)\n• Move to Sales (redirect)\n• Cancel",
