    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "c_rules_text",
      "x": 2250,
      "y": 3376,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "Appointment → CANCELLED\n\nSMS is sent only if the pre-cancel status\nwas SCHEDULED, CONFIRMED, EN_ROUTE,\nor IN_PROGRESS. DRAFT cancels are silent.\n\nOn-site timestamps cleared:\non_my_way_at, started_at,\ncompleted_at, en_route_at.\n\nIf this was the last active appointment\nfor the job, the job reverts to\nTO BE SCHEDULED (from SCHEDULED or\nIN PROGRESS).\n\nA repeat \"C\" from the same customer is\na no-op (no second cancellation SMS).\n\nAdmin is notified.",
      "originalText": "Appointment → CANCELLED\n\nSMS is sent only if the pre-cancel status\nwas SCHEDULED, CONFIRMED, EN_ROUTE,\nor IN_PROGRESS. DRAFT cancels are silent.\n\nOn-site timestamps cleared:\non_my_way_at, started_at,\ncompleted_at, en_route_at.\n\nIf this was the last active appointment\nfor the job, the job reverts to\nTO BE SCHEDULED (from SCHEDULED or\nIN PROGRESS).\n\nA repeat \"C\" from the same customer is\na no-op (no second cancellation SMS).\n\nAdmin is notified.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#7f1d1d",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 800013,
