      "y": 4460,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "ONE-OFF JOB — payment options\n\n•  \"Pay with Card (Tap to Pay)\"\n    → Stripe Terminal NFC via phone\n•  \"Record Other Payment\"\n    → Cash, Check, Venmo, Zelle\n•  \"Create Invoice\"\n    → customer pays later\n\nAfter tap-to-pay: SMS / email receipt\nprompt.",
      "originalText": "ONE-OFF JOB — payment options\n\n•  \"Pay with Card (Tap to Pay)\"\n    → Stripe Terminal NFC via phone\n•  \"Record Other Payment\"\n    → Cash, Check, Venmo, Zelle\n•  \"Create Invoice\"\n    → customer pays later\n\nAfter tap-to-pay: SMS / email receipt\nprompt.",
