    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cancel_dialog_text",
      "x": 224,
      "y": 3848,
      "width": 792,
      "height": 236,
      "text": "A confirmation dialog opens showing customer name, phone, date, and time.\nIt has TWO action buttons:\n\n   ▸  \"Cancel (no text)\"  — cancels the appointment and SUPPRESSES the cancellation SMS.\n      Use when you've already called the customer or when the SMS shouldn't go out.\n\n   ▸  \"Cancel & text customer\"  — cancels and SENDS the cancellation SMS.\n\nBoth choices are audit-logged with notify_customer = true / false.\n\nPre-cancel status rules:\n   • DRAFT                               →  no SMS either way (customer was never notified)\n   • SCHEDULED / CONFIRMED /  →  default is to text; admin can override\n      EN_ROUTE / IN_PROGRESS\n\nOn-site timestamps cleared. If this was the last active appointment for the job,\nthe job reverts from SCHEDULED or IN_PROGRESS back to TO_BE_SCHEDULED.",
      "originalText": "A confirmation dialog opens showing customer name, phone, date, and time.\nIt has TWO action buttons:\n\n   ▸  \"Cancel (no text)\"  — cancels the appointment and SUPPRESSES the cancellation SMS.\n      Use when you've already called the customer or when the SMS shouldn't go out.\n\n   ▸  \"Cancel & text customer\"  — cancels and SENDS the cancellation SMS.\n\nBoth choices are audit-logged with notify_customer = true / false.\n\nPre-cancel status rules:\n   • DRAFT                               →  no SMS either way (customer was never notified)\n   • SCHEDULED / CONFIRMED /  →  default is to text; admin can override\n      EN_ROUTE / IN_PROGRESS\n\nOn-site timestamps cleared. If this was the last active appointment for the job,\nthe job reverts from SCHEDULED or IN_PROGRESS back to TO_BE_SCHEDULED.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#7f1d1d",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1200009,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1200010,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": "cancel_dialog_box",
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
