    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "admin_action3_body",
      "x": 210,
      "y": 4430,
      "width": 820,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "Trigger: rescheduling from the Reschedule Requests queue after a prior \"C\" reply,\nor dragging a cancelled card back onto the calendar.\n\nSame reschedule notification SMS is sent so the customer knows the appointment is back on.\nStatus → SCHEDULED. Customer confirms again with Y / R / C.",
