      "x": 220,
      "y": 4636,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 68,
      "text": "Trigger: Invoices tab mass notification on past-due invoices.\n\"[Customer name], invoice #[number] for $[amount] was due on [date] and is now past due.\nPlease remit payment at your earliest convenience.\"   (replies go to the general inbox)",
